A mole on or near the left Dug in a man, fignifies he ſhall
indanger himſelf by raſh actions, and may happen to die an untimely death;
and much to the ſame purpoſe is its ſignification in a woman.

A mole on the right ſide, ſomewhat above
• he lower part of the member, concludes a man fortunate, eſpecially in Marriage;
and a woman in her Friends and Relations.
